content_sections.content:
Nested If Statements
You can also have
if
statements inside
if
statements, this is called
nested
if
statements.
Example
x <- 41
if (x > 10) {
print("Above ten")
if (x > 
  20) {
print("and also above 20!")
} else {
print("but not above 20.")
}
} else {
print("below 
  10.")
}

